      it can
      utilize the href attribute and/or the onclick attribute with a script. See the constants
    </description>
    <name>toolbarcell</name>
    <tag-class>labware.web.component.toolbar.ToolBarCellTag</tag-class>
    <body-content>JSP</body-content>
    <attribute>
